**CIPHER_NET** is an immersive **Capture The Flag (CTF)** web application designed to simulate a hostile digital environment. Users act as agents penetrating a secure network by solving varying levels of cryptographic puzzlesâ€”from classical ciphers to modern file-based steganography.

